rComments: His lectures are engaging and he encourages class participation.  Take thorough notes from his lectures as he doesn't post anything online.  Attend class and do the readings if you want to pass this class.
I've taken a few courses with Professor Rockel and he is very knowledgable and approachable! One of the best professors I've had at UTSC!

Lectures were not always very clear. However, he is very approachable and willing to assist if you ask. I received an extension on my final paper as per a prior arrangement. He was always there to answer any question and help when he could!
